{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":560,"text":"This is my nephew,"},{"time":3280,"text":"Yuan Yuan."},{"time":4600,"text":"He's five years old,"},{"time":6120,"text":"super adorable."},{"time":8360,"text":"I asked him the other day,"},{"time":10360,"text":"\"What would you like\nfor your birthday this year?\""},{"time":13360,"text":"He said, \"I want to have\na one-way mirror Spider-Man mask.\""},{"time":18000,"text":"I had absolutely no idea\nwhat he was talking about,"},{"time":20800,"text":"so I said, \"Wow, that's really cool,"},{"time":22800,"text":"but how are you going to get it?\""},{"time":25120,"text":"He told me, without a blink of his eyes,"},{"time":28040,"text":"\"I'm going to tell my mom\nand make a wish before I go to bed."},{"time":32759,"text":"My mom will go to shake her mobile phone."},{"time":35400,"text":"The next morning, the delivery uncle\nwill give it to me when I wake up.\""},{"time":41320,"text":"I was about to tease him,"},{"time":43320,"text":"but suddenly I realized"},{"time":45120,"text":"he was simply telling me the truth,"},{"time":47480,"text":"the truth of what shopping\nlooks like for this generation."}]},{"cues":[{"time":51640,"text":"If you think of it,\nfor a child like Yuan Yuan,"},{"time":55280,"text":"shopping is a very different idea"},{"time":57600,"text":"compared to what\nmy generation had in mind."},{"time":60520,"text":"Shopping is always done on mobile,"},{"time":62800,"text":"and payment is all virtual."}]},{"cues":[{"time":66000,"text":"A huge shopping revolution\nis happening in China right now."},{"time":71120,"text":"Shopping behaviors,\nand also technology platforms,"},{"time":75000,"text":"have evolved differently\nthan elsewhere in the world."},{"time":77880,"text":"For instance, e-commerce\nin China is soaring."},{"time":81800,"text":"It's been growing at twice the speed\nof the United States"},{"time":84640,"text":"and a lot of the growth\nis coming from mobile."},{"time":87920,"text":"Every month, 500 million consumers"},{"time":92720,"text":"are buying on mobile phones,"},{"time":94840,"text":"and to put that into context,"},{"time":96600,"text":"that is a total population\nof the United States,"},{"time":99840,"text":"UK and Germany combined."},{"time":103040,"text":"But it is not just about\nthe scale of the e-commerce,"},{"time":106920,"text":"it is the speed of adoption\nand the aggregation of the ecosystems."},{"time":111520,"text":"It took China less than five years\nto become a country of mobile commerce,"},{"time":116040,"text":"and that is largely because\nof the two technology platforms,"},{"time":121200,"text":"Alibaba and Tencent."},{"time":123120,"text":"They own 90 percent of the e-commerce --"},{"time":126720,"text":"pretty much the whole market --"},{"time":128400,"text":"85 percent of social media,"},{"time":130759,"text":"85 percent of internet payment."},{"time":133920,"text":"And they also own large volumes\nof digital content, video, online movie,"},{"time":140480,"text":"literature, travel information, gaming."},{"time":145200,"text":"When this huge base of mobile shoppers"},{"time":148480,"text":"meets with aggregated ecosystems,"},{"time":150960,"text":"chemical reactions happen."},{"time":152840,"text":"Today, China is like a huge laboratory"},{"time":155480,"text":"generating all sorts of experiments."},{"time":158320,"text":"You should come to China,"},{"time":159800,"text":"because here you will get\na glimpse into the future."}]},{"cues":[{"time":164520,"text":"One of the trends I have seen\nconcerns the spontaneity of shopping."},{"time":169440,"text":"Five years ago, in a fashion study,"},{"time":171520,"text":"we found that on average,"},{"time":173000,"text":"a Chinese consumer would be buying\nfive to eight pairs of shoes."},{"time":176960,"text":"This number tripled\nto reach about 25 pairs of shoes a year."},{"time":181360,"text":"Who would need so many pairs of shoes?"},{"time":184520,"text":"So I asked them,\n\"What are the reasons you buy?\""},{"time":187680,"text":"They told me a list of inspirations:"},{"time":190360,"text":"blogs, celebrity news,\nfashion information."},{"time":195040,"text":"But really, for many of them,\nthere was no particular reason to buy."},{"time":198520,"text":"They were just browsing\non their mobile site"},{"time":201040,"text":"and then buying whatever they saw."},{"time":204560,"text":"We have observed the same level\nof spontaneity in everything,"},{"time":208840,"text":"from grocery shopping\nto buying insurance products."},{"time":214240,"text":"But it is not very difficult\nto understand if you think about it."},{"time":217840,"text":"A lot of the Chinese consumers\nare still very new"},{"time":220600,"text":"in their middle-class\nor upper-middle-class lifestyles,"},{"time":223840,"text":"with a strong desire\nto buy everything new,"},{"time":226840,"text":"new products, new services."},{"time":228920,"text":"And with this integrated ecosystem,"},{"time":231640,"text":"it is so easy for them to buy,\none click after another."},{"time":237520,"text":"However, this new shopping behavior\nis creating a lot of challenges"},{"time":242040,"text":"for those once-dominant businesses."},{"time":244800,"text":"The owner of a fashion company\ntold me that he's so frustrated"},{"time":248680,"text":"because his customers keep complaining\nthat his products are not new enough."},{"time":253320,"text":"Well, for a fashion company,\nreally bad comment."},{"time":257519,"text":"And he already increased the number\nof products in each collection."},{"time":261000,"text":"It doesn't seem to work."},{"time":262800,"text":"So I told him there's something\nmore important than that."},{"time":266240,"text":"You've got to give your consumer\nexactly what they want"},{"time":269720,"text":"when they still want it."},{"time":271720,"text":"And he can learn something\nfrom the online apparel players in China."},{"time":276280,"text":"These companies, they collect\nreal consumer feedback"},{"time":279560,"text":"from mobile sites, from social media,"},{"time":282080,"text":"and then their designers\nwill translate this information"},{"time":285400,"text":"into product ideas,"},{"time":287120,"text":"and then send them\nto microstudios for production."},{"time":291160,"text":"These microstudios are really key\nin this overall ecosystem,"},{"time":295000,"text":"because they take small orders,"},{"time":297200,"text":"30 garments at a time,"},{"time":299400,"text":"and they can also make\npartially customized pieces."},{"time":303800,"text":"The fact that all these production designs"},{"time":307000,"text":"are done locally,"},{"time":308480,"text":"the whole process, from transporting\nto product on shelf or online"},{"time":313040,"text":"sometimes takes only three to four days."},{"time":315640,"text":"That is super fast,"},{"time":317360,"text":"and that is highly responsive\nto what is in and hot on the market."},{"time":321000,"text":"And that is giving enormous headaches\nto traditional retailers"},{"time":325320,"text":"who are only thinking\nabout a few collections a year."}]},{"cues":[{"time":330280,"text":"Then there's a consumer's need\nfor ultraconvenience."},{"time":334240,"text":"A couple of months ago,\nI was shopping with a friend in Tokyo."},{"time":337480,"text":"We were in the store,"},{"time":338760,"text":"and there were three to four people\nstanding in front of us"},{"time":341600,"text":"at the checkout counter."},{"time":343080,"text":"Pretty normal, right?"},{"time":344640,"text":"But both of us dropped our selection"},{"time":347440,"text":"and walked away."},{"time":349440,"text":"This is how impatient we have become."},{"time":352560,"text":"Delivering ultraconvenience\nis not just something nice to have."},{"time":356440,"text":"It is crucial to make sure\nyour consumer actually buys."},{"time":360360,"text":"And in China, we have learned"},{"time":362560,"text":"that convenience is really the glue\nthat will make online shopping"},{"time":366720,"text":"a behavior and a habit that sticks."},{"time":369720,"text":"It is sometimes more effective\nthan a loyalty program alone."},{"time":373320,"text":"Take Hema."},{"time":375040,"text":"It's a retail grocery concept\ndeveloped by Alibaba."},{"time":379600,"text":"They deliver a full basket of products"},{"time":381600,"text":"from 4,000 SKUs to your doorstep"},{"time":384880,"text":"within 30 minutes."},{"time":386760,"text":"What is amazing is that they deliver\nliterally everything:"},{"time":390880,"text":"fruits, vegetables, of course."},{"time":393120,"text":"They also deliver live fish"},{"time":395480,"text":"and also live Alaska king crab."},{"time":398960,"text":"Like my friend once told me,"},{"time":401240,"text":"\"It's really my dream coming true."},{"time":402960,"text":"Finally, I can impress my mother-in-law"},{"time":405920,"text":"when she comes to visit me\nfor dinner unexpectedly.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":408920,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":412240,"text":"Well, companies\nlike Amazon and FreshDirect"},{"time":414920,"text":"are also experimenting in the same field."},{"time":417840,"text":"The fact that Hema\nis part of the Alibaba ecosystem"},{"time":421440,"text":"makes it faster and also\na bit easier to implement."},{"time":425760,"text":"For an online grocery player,"},{"time":427680,"text":"it is very difficult, very costly,"},{"time":430520,"text":"to deliver a full basket quickly,"},{"time":433320,"text":"but for Hema, it's got a mobile app,"},{"time":435960,"text":"it's got mobile payment,"},{"time":437640,"text":"and also it's built 20 physical stores\nin high-density areas in Shanghai."},{"time":443360,"text":"These stores are built\nto ensure the freshness of the product --"},{"time":447280,"text":"they actually have\nfish tanks in the store --"},{"time":450200,"text":"and also to give locations\nthat will enable high-speed delivery."},{"time":454920,"text":"I know the question you have on your mind."},{"time":456960,"text":"Are they making money?"},{"time":458240,"text":"Yes, they are making money."},{"time":459600,"text":"They are breaking even,"},{"time":460880,"text":"and what is also amazing\nis that the sales revenue per store"},{"time":464480,"text":"is three to four times higher\nthan the traditional grocery store,"},{"time":468520,"text":"and half of the revenue orders\nare coming from mobile."},{"time":473040,"text":"This is really proof that a consumer,"},{"time":475920,"text":"if you give them ultraconvenience\nthat really works in grocery shopping,"},{"time":479520,"text":"they're going to switch\ntheir shopping behaviors online,"},{"time":482400,"text":"like, in no time."}]},{"cues":[{"time":485480,"text":"So ultraconvenience and spontaneity,"},{"time":488600,"text":"that's not the full story."},{"time":490480,"text":"The other trend I have seen in China"},{"time":492640,"text":"is social shopping."},{"time":494440,"text":"If you think of social shopping\nelsewhere in the world,"},{"time":497080,"text":"it is a linear process."},{"time":499560,"text":"You pick up something on Facebook,"},{"time":501720,"text":"watch it, and you switch to Amazon"},{"time":504360,"text":"or brand.com to complete\nthe shopping journey."},{"time":507080,"text":"Clean and simple."},{"time":508760,"text":"But in China it is a very different thing."},{"time":511880,"text":"On average, a consumer would spend\none hour on their mobile phone shopping."},{"time":516640,"text":"That's three times higher\nthan the United States."},{"time":519320,"text":"Where does the stickiness come from?"},{"time":521280,"text":"What are they actually doing\non this tiny little screen?"},{"time":525120,"text":"So let me take you\non a mobile shopping journey"},{"time":527600,"text":"that I usually would be experiencing."}]},{"cues":[{"time":531000,"text":"11pm, yes, that's usually when I shop."},{"time":534800,"text":"I was having a chat in a WeChat\nchatroom with my friends."},{"time":538440,"text":"One of them took out a pack of snack"},{"time":540560,"text":"and posted the product link\nin that chatroom."},{"time":544320,"text":"I hate it, because usually\nI would just click that link"},{"time":548040,"text":"and then land on the product page."},{"time":550680,"text":"Lots of information, very colorful,"},{"time":552960,"text":"mind-blowing."},{"time":554400,"text":"Watched it and then\na shop assistant came online"},{"time":557160,"text":"and asked me, \"How can I\nhelp you tonight?\""},{"time":560240,"text":"Of course I bought that pack of snack."},{"time":562440,"text":"What is more beautiful is I know\nthat the next day, around noontime,"},{"time":566520,"text":"that pack of snack\nwill be delivered to my office."},{"time":569400,"text":"I can eat it and share it\nwith my colleagues"},{"time":572040,"text":"and the cost of delivery,\nmaximum one dollar."}]},{"cues":[{"time":576240,"text":"Just when I was about to leave\nthat shopping site,"},{"time":579200,"text":"another screen popped up."},{"time":581080,"text":"This time it is the livestreaming\nof a grassroots celebrity"},{"time":585760,"text":"teaching me how to wear\na new color of lipstick."},{"time":589040,"text":"I watched for 30 seconds --\nvery easy to understand --"},{"time":592160,"text":"and also there is\na shopping link right next to it,"},{"time":595240,"text":"clicked it, bought it in a few seconds."}]},{"cues":[{"time":598600,"text":"Back to the chatroom."},{"time":600120,"text":"The gossiping is still going on."},{"time":602000,"text":"Another friend of mine posted the QR code"},{"time":604880,"text":"of another pack of snack."},{"time":606560,"text":"Clicked it, bought it."},{"time":609080,"text":"So the whole experience"},{"time":610680,"text":"is like you're exploring\nin an amusement park."},{"time":614480,"text":"It is chaotic, it is fun"},{"time":617120,"text":"and it's even a little bit addictive."},{"time":620520,"text":"This is what's happening\nwhen you have this integrated ecosystem."},{"time":624960,"text":"Shopping is embedded in social,"},{"time":627680,"text":"and social is evolving\ninto a multidimensional experience."},{"time":632400,"text":"The integration of ecosystems\nreaches a whole new level."},{"time":636120,"text":"So does its dominance\nin all aspects of our life."}]},{"cues":[{"time":640720,"text":"And of course, there are huge\ncommercial opportunities behind it."},{"time":644360,"text":"A Chinese snack company, Three Squirrels,"},{"time":647200,"text":"built a half-a-billion-dollar business\nin just three years"},{"time":651000,"text":"by investing in 300 to 500 shop assistants"},{"time":654840,"text":"who are going to be online\nto provide services 24/7."},{"time":659000,"text":"In the social media environment,"},{"time":661040,"text":"they are like your neighborhood friends."},{"time":663000,"text":"Even when you are not buying stuff,"},{"time":664720,"text":"they will be happy to just tell you\na few jokes and make you happy."},{"time":669000,"text":"In this integrated ecosystem,"},{"time":671120,"text":"social media can really redefine\nthe relationship between brand,"},{"time":675600,"text":"retailer and consumer."}]},{"cues":[{"time":679440,"text":"These are only fragments\nof the massive changes"},{"time":682920,"text":"I have seen in China."},{"time":684640,"text":"In this huge laboratory,"},{"time":686640,"text":"a lot of experiments\nare generated every single day."},{"time":691040,"text":"The ecosystems are reforming,"},{"time":693560,"text":"supply chain distribution,\nmarketing, product innovation,"},{"time":697760,"text":"everything."},{"time":699000,"text":"Consumers are getting the power\nto decide what they want to buy,"},{"time":703280,"text":"when they want to buy it,"},{"time":704600,"text":"how they want to buy it,\nhow they want to social."},{"time":707640,"text":"It is now back to business\nleaders of the world"},{"time":711080,"text":"to really open their eyes,\nsee what's happening in China,"},{"time":714440,"text":"think about it and take actions."}]},{"cues":[{"time":718320,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":719560,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":727760,"text":"Massimo Portincaso: Angela, \nwhat you shared with us"},{"time":730260,"text":"is truly impressive and almost incredible,"},{"time":732400,"text":"but I think many in the audience\nhad the same question that I had,"},{"time":737680,"text":"which is:"},{"time":738920,"text":"Is this kind of impulsive consumption"},{"time":742280,"text":"both economically and environmentally\nsustainable over the longer term?"},{"time":746520,"text":"And what is the total price to be paid"},{"time":750280,"text":"for such an automized\nand ultraconvenient retail experience?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":755000,"text":"Angela Wang: Yeah.\nOne thing we have to keep in mind"},{"time":757920,"text":"is really, we are at the very beginning\nof a huge transformation."},{"time":762200,"text":"So with this trading up\nneeds of the consumer,"},{"time":765360,"text":"together with the evolution\nof the ecosystem,"},{"time":768520,"text":"there are a lot of opportunities\nand also challenges."},{"time":772320,"text":"So I've seen some early signs"},{"time":773920,"text":"that the ecosystems\nare shifting their focus"},{"time":776800,"text":"to pay attention\nto solve these challenges."},{"time":779400,"text":"For example, paying more\nconsideration to sustainability"},{"time":783680,"text":"alongside just about speed,"},{"time":785640,"text":"and also quality over quantity."},{"time":788520,"text":"But there are really\nno simple answers to these questions."},{"time":791480,"text":"That is exactly why\nI'm here to tell everyone"},{"time":794120,"text":"that we need to watch it, study it,\nand play a part in this evolution."}]},{"cues":[{"time":799680,"text":"MP: Thank you very much."}]},{"cues":[{"time":801240,"text":"AW: Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":802480,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}